title: $:/plugins/tobibeer/toc/readme

The plugin $:/plugins/tobibeer/toc provides:

; toc[]
: a filter to fetch tiddlers in a toc

; Operand
: defines the root title
: defaults to the value of `<<currentTiddler>>`

; Suffixes
: are declared as `name=<value>`...
: `level=<number>`
: `exclude=variableName`
: `truncate=variableName`
: `list=field-name`
: `sort=field-name` ASC or `sort=!field-name` DESC

